Your influence marketing agency

   Big influencers have a larger audience than the world cup football
   final* and a power of persuasion that is 10 times bigger than classic
   advertising approaches**

   If you are not using influence marketing as an advertising tool, you
   are probably not reaching your target audience

Looking for expertise?

   Influence4you has existed since 2012 when the term "Youtuber" was
   almost unheard of. We have since carried out more than 5000 projects
   with top influencers or with thousands of micro-influencers.

   Our 45 international experts know everything there is to know about
   influence marketing. We are recognised as THE project managers that
   know how to deliver, especially when influence marketing can be
   unpredictable (managing talents, fake followers, ...)
   Looking for expertise?
   Pandora, increase sales for Valentines Day
   Pandora, increase sales for Valentines Day

Are you looking for local or international guidance?

   An International group or SME that has understood that television, news
   or radio is no longer an effective method to reach 15-40 year olds, we
   work with the most stylish brands (and their agencies) in more than 30
   countries to manage their influencers (top influencers,
   micro-influencers,...)
   Our teams will be able to find you strategies which will have the
   largest impact on social media (Instagram, Youtube, Facebook, Twitter,
   Pinterest, …)
   +33 1 80 88 97 12 Contact us

Looking for great results?

   In line with your communication strategy, our experts launch tailor
   made campaigns corresponding to YOUR objectives (notoriety, engagement,
   traffic, recruitment, content creation, ...

   Our data on 37 million profiles, as well as the integration of
   Hypeauditor, a tool allowing for identification of fake followers,
   allows us to launch campaigns which will generate the best results.
   Following the project, you will receive a thorough report (see example)
   detailing the Earned Media Value of the operation.
   The body Shop - visiting farmers in Rwanda
   The body Shop - visiting farmers in Rwanda
   MSC Cruise, influencers sent on a round the world trip
   MSC Cruise, influencers sent on a round the world trip

Looking to save time?

   In line with your agency and your team, our project managers find
   influencers world wide, write the campaign brief which is validated by
   yourselves, negotiate contracts with influencers, manage the campaign
   from A - Z, create end of operation reports and look after the
   administrative side
   This allows you to simply concentrate on your communication strategy
   and the approval of our work. Let us look after all the time-consuming
   tasks in the world of influence marketing, whilst focusing on the
   essential: your business!
   Contact us
